             sworn. - On Monday, the 3d of July, I saw the prisoner take a pocket-book out of Mr. Beach's pocket, about half past twelve o'clock at noon, upon <placeName id="t17970712-7-crimeloc38">Ludgate-hill</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17970712-7-crimeloc38" type="placeName" value="Ludgate-hill"></interp>
