                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17970712-7-off36 t17970712-7-crimeloc38"></join>; the constable has the pocket-book here; I took hold of him, and delivered him to the constable.</p>
               <p>Q. Do you know the prosecutor's name? - A. Yes; John Beach.</p>
               <p>JOHN VINIE sworn. - I am a constable: (produces the pocket-book); it was delivered to me by the last witness.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's defence. I was walking along when this man charged me with stealing the pocket-book; I did not do any such thing.</p>
               <p>The prisoner called six witnesses, who gave him a good character.</p>
               <p>
